<P><HI>Dulne&s;s made</HI>] This pa&s;&s;age may be properly illu&s;trated by a recollection of two lines in Mr. POPE's e&s;&s;ay on critici&s;m.</P>
<Q><L>As things &s;eem large which we thro' mi&s;ts de&s;ecy,</L>
<L>Dulne&s;s is very apt to magnify.</L></Q>
