<P><HI>A full di&s;charge,</HI>] Reader do not turn up your no&s;e at this pa&s;&s;age! it is much more decent th$n POPE's&mdash;Recollect what SWIFT &s;ays, that a nice man has filthy ideas, and let it be con|&s;idered &s;idered this di&s;charge may have the &s;ame effect upon our hero, as a &s;imilar accident had upon a per&s;on of equal parts and genius.</P>
<Q><L>Renew'd by ordure's &s;ympathetic force,</L>
